      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved specimen, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle exhibits a pristine aesthetic and mechanical profile, reflective of a life spent under meticulous stewardship. Featuring a showroom-quality finish and unrivaled performance consistency, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection. Every detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets our rigorous criteria for absolute excellence.",
