    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible showroom condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I've babied it since day one, keeping it garage-kept and professionally detailed. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. You won't find one cleaner than this!",
