      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, currently held in pristine, showroom condition. This specimen has been curated with exacting standards, manifesting in an interior and exterior that remain indistinguishable from its original production state. Every mechanical system has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering a driving experience defined by absolute precision and refinement. For the discerning individual seeking an investment-grade vehicle that transcends the standard pre-owned market, this offering represents the pinnacle of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 47500.0,
