      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this absolute beauty in person! It's a total dream and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've absolutely babied this car from day one\u2014it's spotless inside and out, runs like a top, and has always been kept tucked away in a garage. If you're looking for that perfect, like-new feel without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
