    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example is powered by the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS timing, mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical integrity is absolute: the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearings have been replaced to ensure long-term reliability. The chassis remains exceptionally communicative, benefiting from a factory-spec limited-slip differential and untouched OEM suspension geometry. Finished in its original paint with zero imperfections, the car sits on flawless Style 67 forged wheels. Inside, the Nappa leather bolsters show no signs of compression or wear, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and meticulous stewardship.",
